<br>
1) You can buy from anyone directly from the list without having to find them (this way I can stare at the wall)*.<br>
<br>
2) Money automaticaly taken out of your bank to pay for items while you are in /bazaar mode (see *)<br>
<br>
3) Ideally allow folks to go in to /bazaar mode anywhere. To sell you have to have a traders satchel on you as you do now. To buy if you are not in the bazaar you have to have the money on you. Hell this way I can avoid the bazaar.<br>
<br>
Of course number 3 has issues of defeating quests. Place someone near the person who gives part 1, someone near part 2 etc and off we go, sell for a copper and the item moves between us. So really 3 would not be allowed.<br>
